787
00:53:39,440 --> 00:53:41,420
<font color=#00FF00>Selanjutnya aku pergi ke Yunkai.</font>

788
00:53:41,650 --> 00:53:43,650
<font color=#00FF00>Mereka yang dulu budak di Yunkai,</font>

789
00:53:44,600 --> 00:53:46,755
<font color=#00FF00>sekarang berdiri di belakangku,</font>

790
00:53:47,690 --> 00:53:48,437
<font color=#00FF00>bebas.</font>

791
00:53:51,295 --> 00:53:53,335
<font color=#00FF00>Sekarang aku datang ke Meereen.</font>

792
00:53:55,134 --> 00:53:58,221
<font color=#00FF00>Aku bukan musuhmu.</font>

793
00:53:58,372 --> 00:54:01,850
<font color=#00FF00>Musuh berada di sampingmu,</font>

794
00:54:02,600 --> 00:54:07,253
<font color=#00FF00>Musuh mu mencuri dan membununuh anak kalian.</font>

795
00:54:08,511 --> 00:54:12,460
